desc_long									特色列表									Current features in the early access build:Fast 3D graphics with shadows, FXAA, and optinal toon effectsMultiplayer over LAN/Internet TCPProcedurally generated, persistent worldsWorld streaming in all directions, including up and downCrafting of weapons, armor, and miscellaneous itemsDay & Night affecting unit statsUnit attributes, skills, and talentsSlot-based inventory systemGrid based digging and buildingItem quality and material affecting weapon and armor effectivnessOptional scaling of difficulty by crafting totems in-game, increasing XP gain in returnStreamlined interfaceCustomizable shaders, textures, and modelsRandomly generated dungeonsRandomized alchemy using a scripting language and thus easily being customizableD&D-like high effect magic, scripted as wellUnique, optional "Communications mode"Different playable races with special perksMechanics system (traps, gates via lever)																						关于这款游戏							Dungeoncraft is a fantasy real time strategy game featuring multiplayer sandbox survival type gameplay, dynamic world expansion, and 3D grid based digging and building.It does allow for direct control over your units, having indirect orders only for convenience' sake.Craft weapons, raid dungeons for epic loot and mighty spells, brew potions, build or dig fortifications against the computer or your friends. It's all up to you!Play in the unique "Communications Mode", which only allows you to control your units if you supply them with orders or contact them directly with your avatar or substitutes!						
